
'''= PicoMoney is a platform for creating tradable, transparent, and vibrant virtual currencies for your business, open source project, association, or even yourself.'''

URL = https://picomoney.com/


=Description

Open source projects and charities can issue publicly viewable Karma currencies to their contributors. Companies can publicly show support for these projects by exchanging Karma currencies for their own currencies.

Our whole platform is open to developers. You will be able to create your applications such as GitKarma with built in ways of monetizing your apps. More on this soon, but you can already get started now if you are adventurous with our API which is based on the new [[Open Transact]] payment standard.


